{
  "texts": [
    "In particular, for each of our 11 occupations, we conducted a workplace-based sampling procedure, first drawing a random set of workplaces within each occupation and then sampling all relevant workers at these workplaces.",
    "This sampling procedure maximizes the statistical power of the workplace-level analyses while keeping our sample representative.",
    "Appendix B.1 details the sampling protocol.",
    "We sent three reminders per survey round, two by e-mail and one by text.",
    "The invitation letters are in Appendix I."
  ]
}